{"word":"ἑκατοντάρχης","slug":"ἑκατοντάρχης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἑϰατοντάρχης, ου</el></b> <b>/</b> <b><el>ἑϰατόνταρχος, ου, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a></el></b> [<el>ἕϰατον, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄρχω\">ἄρχω</a></el>] Roman military officer (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> centurio) ranking below a tribune and commanding about a hundred men, <b>centurion, captain:</b> -<el>ης</el> <b><a href='B:470 8:13'>Mt 8:13</a>; <a href='B:490 7:6'>Lk 7:6</a>; <a href='B:490 23:47'>23:47</a>; <a href='B:510 10:1'>Ac 10:1</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Ac; <b>-</b><el>ος</el> <b><a href='B:470 8:5'>Mt 8:5</a>, <a href='B:470 8:8'>8</a>; <a href='B:510 22:25'>Ac 22:25</a>; <a href='B:510 28:16'>28:16</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἑκατονταπλασίων\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκβαίνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}